articles.title: Olympic gold medalist Tori Bowie dies aged 32 - CNN
articles.description: American sprinter and long jumper Tori Bowie -- a three-time Olympic medalist and a two-time world champion in track and field -- has died, according to her agent, Kimberly Holland. Bowie was 32 years old.
